        WEB_SITE=http://zengarden.foo-projects.org/
         ENTERED=20050115
         UPDATED=20050115
       BUILD_API=2
        KEYWORDS="utils"
           SHORT="zengarden is a utility for tracking files during the installation of software."
cat << EOF
zengarden is a tool that watches over the installation and building of
source archives.  It is a fork of installwatch that has been heavily updated
with modern features.  It can prevent build tools from interfering with
files outside the build directory and create a virtual chroot to perform
installations in or backup the files the install overwrites.
EOF
